snippet.title: Luna's Fishing Garden - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1477790/Lunas_Fishing_Garden/

Coldwild Games is happy to present you Luna's Fishing Garden!

Luna’s Fishing Garden is a cozy fishing and building game.

Catch more than 20 types of fish, each with their own behavior, trade in the resources to Luna, and use them to build a garden of your dreams, all taking place on an imaginary Pacific archipelago. Designed to be a relaxing experience, players can play at their own pace and experience the game how they like it. 


Planned release date on March 2, 2021, wishlist today to get notified on release!
Art created by illufinch ( https://twitter.com/illufinch/ )
Trailer Music by Paul Zimmermann ( http://soundcloud.com/paulzimmermann/ )
